
=== Attribute ==============================================

inst_column_width: <size>               # Set instance column width (default: 32)

=== Group Summation ========================================

g:<gid>:<group_name>                    # Create a summation group (gid: group ID)

=== Instance Choose ========================================

p:[did]:<path>[:option]                 # Choose instance by the absolute path
r:[did]:<path>[:option]                 # Choose instance by the regular expression

- did : design id
    - keep empty means choose path from all designs

- option
    - inf : choose instances by break down to leaf nodes from the specific instance
    - <n> : choose instances by break down n levels from the specific instance

=== Instance Operation =====================================

<inst_path> sum                         # Leaf trace and sum the areas from the specific instance
<inst_path> sr                          # Separate and become a sub design tree from the main design tree 
<inst_path> rn:<name>                   # Rename instance path
                                            - path/inst view : replace instance path
                                            - tree view      : replace basename

<inst_path> add:<gid>                   # Add area to the specific group
<inst_path> sub:<gid>                   # Substract area from the specific group

<inst_path> show[:condition]            # show the instance from the area display
<inst_path> hide[:condition]            # Hide the instance from the area display

- condition format : <target><operation><value>
    - target     : att (absolute total), ptt (percent total)
    - operation  : >, <, ==, >=, <=
    - value type : float
- priority : show > hide > default

